title: Thair Jassam
text:
Thair Jassam Homi (born 31 December 1959) is a coach and former Iraqi <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player, also a coach.
Jassam signed to manage <a href="Al-Najaf%20FC">Al-Najaf</a> in the Iraqi premier league in November 9 of 2018, and is still leading the Najaf city team.
Honours.
Club.
